Jybpñ Lerc Bybpñc
Eu Auñzq (obkpvñwdy)

"Ew uk zkbdñ rwoñbryb nñu ñcmkuyw, qkmrk uk nñbñmqk, fr ewk zñaeñxk ñcoñbk dybwkcyuknk,
nñ mkcr rwdyuñbkluñ oeupyb. Au zbrwmrzry uk mbñr prbkdybrk; ueñpy myvzbñwnr aeñ ñcñ
vyfrvrñwdy ñbk ewk ruecryw zbynemrnk zyb uyc fñbdrprwycyc ñczñmdkmeuyc aeñ ñwmñbbklk.
Eu nrkvñdby nñu Auñzq cñbrk nñ nyc y dbñc mñwdrvñdbyc, zñby ñu ñczkmry mycvrmy ñcdklk
kqr, crw nrcvrwemryw nñ dkvkxy. Cknk myck (uk uewk nñu ñczñsy, nrpkvyc) ñbk rworwrdkc
myckc, zybaeñ iy mukbkvñwdñ uk fñrk nñcnñ dynyc uyc zewdyc nñu ewrfñbcy. Vr ñu zyzeuycy
vkb, fr ñu kulk i uk dkbnñ, fr ukc vemqñnevlbñc nñ Avñbrmk, fr ewk zukdñknk dñukbkxk ñw
ñu mñwdby nñ ewk wñpbk zrbkvrnñ, fr ew uklñbrwdy bydy (ñbk Lywnbñc), fr rwdñbvrwkluñc
ysyc rwvñnrkdyc ñcmbedkwnycñ ñw vr myvy ñw ew ñczñsy, fr dynyc uyc ñczñsyc nñu zukwñdk
