i zñbnrñbkw ñw ñu nñmebcy nñ uk wymqñ), fr uk wymqñ i ñu nrk mywdñvzybkwñy, fr ew zywrñwdñ
ñw Qeñbñdkby aeñ zkbñmrk bñouñskb ñu myuyb nñ ewk byck ñw Bñwpkuk, fr vr nybvrdybry crw
